## WEEK 2 PHASE 3 CODE CHALLENGE 
- Create three files named Reviews, Customer, and restaurant
- Create classes for each and initialize them
- create lists for customers, reviews, and restuarants and append new ones into the list when added
- return the number of reviews given by a particular customer using a class method
-return thr average rating of a restuarant 
- write a function that finds a given name using a class method
-write a fuction that finds the first customer whose name matches a given name using a class method
